So app grouping is good.

00:04:09.086 --> 00:04:10.416 A:middle
It keeps notifications more

00:04:10.416 --> 00:04:11.626 A:middle
organized and Notification

00:04:11.626 --> 00:04:13.286 A:middle
Center more compact and easier

00:04:13.286 --> 00:04:13.776 A:middle
