00:04:14.466 --> 00:04:17.726 A:middle
But many apps have more specific

00:04:17.726 --> 00:04:18.245 A:middle
content.

00:04:18.536 --> 00:04:20.136 A:middle
They may need different

00:04:20.136 --> 00:04:21.716 A:middle
